                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "The \"Intellectual Property Right Scheme\" under the \"MSME Innovative Scheme\" implemented by the Ministry of Micro, Small & Medium Enterprises, offers legal and intellectual property filing support including patents, trademarks, copyrights, designs, geographical indications (GI) etc. The programme also provides IP advisory, consultation, Patentability Searches, Technology Gap Analyses and IP commercialisation through the establishment of Intellectual Property Facilitation Centres (IPFCs) across the country."
                  }
                ]
