                  {
                    "text": "• Establishment of Intellectual Property Facilitation Centres (IPFCs)."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "• Reimbursement for registration of Patent, Trademark, Geographical Indications (G.I.), Design through IPFCs."
